thread.title: Michael Leonard

author: Michael Leonard
title: Michael Leonard
text:
The guy I talked to was knowledgeable and got the pickup on the way while I was still getting my credit card form filled out. It couldn't have gone better.
Wouldn't have known about you if a local courier didn't know you. I looked up courier service and it did not have your information. Maybe that was the wrong search item.
Great service and arrived in a timely manner on a time-critical item for a piece of equipment that was down.
Great job!!
